title: Caribbean Jerk Beef & Veggie Couscous with Baby Leaves & Mayonnaise
description: The couscous is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh beef in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk seasoning and veggies, then finish off this vibrant and refreshing dinner with a creamy drizzle of mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
